CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 3, 1961, pg. 38 reads: "Newlyweds - Mr. and Mrs. Joseph S. Owens were married, recently, in home of Mrs. Elizabeth V. Hunt, on Lowell St., by the Rev. J.W. Moorehead. The bride is the former Ethel R. Gillus. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Joseph S. Owens and bride Ethel R. Gillus Owens, cutting wedding cake on table with fern decorations in home of Elizabeth V. Hunt, Lowell Street
